headline: Radian Hits 52-Week High: Time to Add the Stock for Better Returns?

headline: NYLI Epoch Global Equity Yield Fund Q1 2025 Commentary
summary: For the quarter, the NYLI Epoch Global Equity Yield Fund posted a return of 3.6% while the broad market returned negative 1.8% as measured by the MSCI World Index.
